-- Bank of America Sued by New York for Losses Tied to Merrill Acquisition
-- Bob Van Voris
-- 2010-07-22T14:15:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/bank-of-america-sued-by-new-york-for-losses-tied-to-merrill-acquisition.html

          
          
             Bank of America Corp. was sued by
New York’s comptroller over losses to the state’s retirement
fund tied to the bank’s acquisition of Merrill Lynch & Co.  
